                        <span>Parent</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#OfferLetter">
                        <img src="~/Images/Admission_Procedure/Offer-Letter.png" alt="" class="img" />
                        <img src="~/Images/Admission_Procedure/Offer-Letter_hover.png" alt="" class="imghover" />
                        <span>Offer Letter</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#Fees">
                        <img src="~/Images/Admission_Procedure/Fees.png" alt="" class="img" />
                        <img src="~/Images/Admission_Procedure/Fees_hover.png" alt="" class="imghover" />
                        <span>Fees</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#WelcomeNote">
                        <img src="~/Images/Admission_Procedure/welcome-Note.png" alt="" class="img" />
                        <img src="~/Images/Admission_Procedure/welcome-Note_hover.png" alt="" class="imghover" />
                        <span>Welcome Note</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="tab-content">
                <div class="tab-pane active" id="Tour">
                    <p>
                        We are eager to welcome new families to the school and show you everything that MLSI has to offer. We are here to assist you with all aspects of the application process, and we take pride in our level of service and personalised attention. Please contact us to make an appointment for a tour.
                    </p>
                    Please keep in mind that the school tour is mandatory.
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="Registration">
                    <p>
                        You can sign up after your tour by paying the registration fee. Fill out the Registration form and attach the following documents:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="checklist">
                        <li>
                            One passport size photograph of the child.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Each parent must provide one passport-sized photograph.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            A photocopy of the child's birth certificate that has been attested.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            A photocopy of the child's proof of permanent and current residence must be attested. (Examples: Passport, Aadhar, etc.)
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Copy of previous two years' school report cards, attested.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            ID proof of both the parents.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="Interaction">
                    After submission of the documents, the admissions team will set up an interview/test with your child.
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="Parent">
                    This is an opportunity for us to meet with parents, understand your family's educational goals for your child, and answer your questions before admission decisions are communicated. The school will send an admission confirmation email based on the parent interaction.
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="OfferLetter">
                    The admission decision will be conveyed to you via email.
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="Fees">
                    In order to formally accept this offer, you must pay the Admission Fee and Caution Money. Please collect and return the completed admission form within one week of receiving the admission offer.
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="WelcomeNote">
                    The admissions team will send an email verifying your admission.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

     

